URL: http://localhost:3333/books
Method:GET
Action: Fetches all the books available in the system.

URL: http://localhost:3000/books/search/:title
Method:GET
Replace :title with the book title you're searching for.
Action: Searches for a book by its title.

URL: http://localhost:3333/books
Method:POST
Action: Adds a new book to the library.

URL: http://localhost:3333/books/request
Method:POST
Action: Student requests a book. If the book is available, they can check it out. If not, they are added to the queue.

URL: http://localhost:3333/books/process-request
Method:POST
Action: Processes the next book request from the queue.